search_results.title: Marvin Terban
search_results.snippet: Marvin I. Terban (born 28 April 1940) is an American children's book author and a long-time educator. Called a master of children's wordplay.

search_results.snippet: Carolyn Marvin is a professor and author that specializes in communication, culture and media, political communication, and technology and society.
